==21830==    by 0x402BC5: main (indent.c:1122)

The cause was that need_chars(&save_com, ...) could reallocate save_com.ptr
pointer keeping a dangling copy of that pointer saved to buf_ptr
a line above.

Related to CVE-2023-40305

